hMailServer password changer plugin for SquirrelMail
====================================================0
Ver 1.1, 2006-10-20

Partly written by Martin Knafve.

This plugin is based on the password changer for MySQL
written by Paul Lesneiwski.

It has been modified to fit for the mailserver hMailServer.
(http://www.hmailserver.com). It uses the hMailServer COM 
library for password modification, so the plugin has to 
be run under Win32.
  
It's necessary that you specify your main hMailServer
password in config.php.